Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.07,0:00:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫咪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还想…多帮点社长忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有事的 这点伤爱西亚会马上治疗…
