Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉雅丝大人的一名“城堡”出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(518,436)}<Rook>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 你竟敢把小猫咪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我下来 我来对付你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静 一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗不能者会被传送到指定的地点接受治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小猫没死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.46,0:02:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管如何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是赢不了我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱乃学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚 这里就交给我 你就先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不必担心 我会全心全意 为小猫报仇雪恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 朱乃学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以来想着有朝一日能跟你单挑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“雷之巫女”小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀 那真是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“爆弹王妃”小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(396,436)}<Boom Queen>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱萨大人的三名“兵卒” 出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(499,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:00.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才所说的三人难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了朱乃学姐的结界 收拾她们让我轻松了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 现在所剩的棋子变为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱萨大人九个 莉雅丝大人五个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木场 抱歉 小猫咪她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.15,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是很内向的女孩子 可今天却干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她心里肯定很怨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去赢得胜利 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑斗 一诚 能听得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爱西亚去奇袭他们大本营
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.65,0:03:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们尽可能的牵制住他们 为我们争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇袭？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.45,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来是计划是 等朱乃的魔力复原后 一个一个去击破
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对方直接派出了“女王”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.19,0:04:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(560,436)}<Queen>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是社长 “王”亲自出击大本营 是不是风险太大？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.10,0:04:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(259,436)}<King>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人也会这么认为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:08.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是抓住这个破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么强调菲尼克斯是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是未必内心也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他尝到足以让他失去战斗意志的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有可能打败莱萨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亲自去挫败莱萨的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就以我们神秘学研究社男子搭档组合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一场华丽的战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我知道你们藏起来的 堂堂正正地滚出来决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莱萨大人的手下“骑士” 卡拉米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(502,436)}<Knight>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然大摇大摆地从正面出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是神智清醒的人的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.33,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我倒是很喜欢 像你们这样的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉雅丝大人的手下“骑士” 木场佑斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.14,0:05:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(517,436)}<Knight>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:07.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“骑士”（Knight）间对决
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直盼着这天到来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得很好 莉雅丝‧吉蒙里的“骑士”！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(615,436)}<Knight>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 话说没有我出场的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉米尔 这人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满脑子都是剑 剑 剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲己方棋子时也摆出愤愤不平的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了她土里土气的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为难得找到了可爱的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他也是剑痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真够不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剩下的棋子全部投入是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长猜对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 莉雅丝看男人的眼光这么差吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长着一副可爱的脸蛋 没想到是个吐毒舌的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“赤龙帝之笼手”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(425,436)}<Boostet Gear>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Boost”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不战的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊莎贝拉 莱萨大人的手下“城堡”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(629,436)}<Rook>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉雅丝点‧吉蒙里的“兵卒”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(578,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那家伙到底算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不战斗到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然作为“主教”参战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(454,436)}<Bishop>
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本只是观战的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…不 那位大人是蕾维儿‧菲尼克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲尼克斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:48.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在是作为眷属 但她是莱萨大人的亲妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这叫做萌自己妹妹？ 不是有很多人羡慕或憧憬有妹妹的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我不萌自己妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是形式上作为我的眷属
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来那鸟混蛋 真的是个白痴变态
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能够充分理解 他想把自己妹妹拉入后宫的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我预计的还强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然 我也不是白白跟小猫和佑斗接受训练的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽这么说 把力量强化到一定程度之前 只有逃跑这一策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Boost”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.40,0:07:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是第五次强化
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是“兵卒”（Pawn）的话 也许足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.42,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是对手是“城堡”的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.44,0:07:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(457,436)}<Rook>
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:41.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 跟以前被米菈袭击时完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来莉雅丝‧吉蒙里把你锻链地训练有素嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我被社长狠狠地训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是莉雅丝社长的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以绝不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只为了社长…也要把你打到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的莉雅丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的食光剑被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾 那种攻击对我是不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这个如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我冻起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙竟然拥有两件神器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们高贵的菲尼克斯眷属 掌管着 火焰 风 生命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输给你这种家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙到底有几件神器？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是拥有多件神器 只是制造出来了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“魔剑制造”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(425,436)}<Sword Birth>
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以按照我的意愿制造出魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来他有那种能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你 战斗中别东张西望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 差不多该来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Boost”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Explosion!!”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力不及“龙之波”的“龙之魔弹”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(380,436)}<Dragon Waves>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(576,436)}<Dragon Shot>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经算是保留了我相当多的力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个神器很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须由我来当场解决掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮着了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样就打中我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我绽开！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“洋服崩坏”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(425,436)}<Dress Break>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在脑内存储器里贴上名片保存
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:09:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保存完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.17,0:10:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莎贝拉被…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱萨大人的“城堡”一名出局
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(443,436)}<Rook>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这招数真够粗暴的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 应该说对女人来说是恐怖的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是头一次看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…该怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉  我们的一诚是个色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别这么毫无掩饰的跟人家道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木场！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你已经注意到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.14,0:10:38.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算主动出击 这也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的诡计被他们拆穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说早就预料到我会来是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.23,0:11:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个处女 可不能小看老练者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉雅丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一成不变 说话还是这么下流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“红发灭杀姬”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(426,436)}<Ruin Princess>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“圣母的微笑”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(424,436)}<Twilight Healing>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“雷之巫女”还有 “魔剑制造”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.07,0:11:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(551,436)}<Sword Birth>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“赤龙帝之笼手”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(424,436)}<Boostet Gear>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是一排听起来很厉害的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们是菲尼克斯不死鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死之身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这情况对于你们来说多么的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蜜 小丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些“兵卒” 你可别光用外表来判断她们的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(225,436)}<Pawn>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“赤龙帝之笼手”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(427,436)}<Boostet Gear>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Boost”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.27,0:11:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.44,0:11:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用下半身思考问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给他狠狠一击 司雷丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下真危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一诚君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你们能多陪我玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是难得的婚前交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见鬼去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.72,0:12:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社长！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.71,0:12:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的事先不说 现在对付眼前的敌人要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信赖着你 一诚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们瞧瞧吉蒙里眷属的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我是社长的仆人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把司雷丝剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手臂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可考虑的 就只为了社长 我要把你们打到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤龙帝啊 如果听得见的话 请回应我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赐予我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Dragon Booster”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更猛烈地回应于我的心意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“赤龙帝之笼手”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(425,436)}<Boostet Gear>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Dragon Booster Second Liberation”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.69,0:13:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形状变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到“雷之巫女”竟然如此的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的魔力 应该早就空了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着你为我担心 因为只要稍微休息一会儿就能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你有那个时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 这是我的新能力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木场！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快释放你的神器的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,释放？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“魔剑制造”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs23\pos(425,436)}<Sword Birth>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“Transfer!!”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs33}莱萨大人的“兵卒”二名 “骑士”二名  “主教”一名 出局
